Mannatech Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback
















mannatech inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Health Care
Industry: Biotech & Pharma
Sub-Industry: Specialty Pharma
Mannatech, Incorporated develops and sells proprietary nutritional supplements and topical products through a network marketing system of independent distributors. The Company's ambrotose complex is an ingredient made from naturally occurring sugars which it includes in its products. Mannatech currently sells its products in the United States, Canada, and Australia.




